{"tid":2298260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住你 但我會忍住唔搵你","createTime":"2020-11-24T02:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T17:41:15.000Z","uid":132160,"like":101,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d110ba2d8d8aebe1f941c1dbe573c38d2cc9c944","tid":2298260,"uid":132160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"見到隔離有個Po話 有冇試過奮不顧身咁愛一個人<br />\n我有架 我真係有試過<br />\n以前一路覺得互相鍾意就咩都得 幾痛都可以繼續行落去<br />\n但當發現有啲野永遠都解決唔到 大家為同一個問題嘈完又嘈<br />\n又或者有啲現實問題 大家只係一直逃避唔敢面對<br />\n咁辛苦行落去對兩邊黎講又係咪好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候 可能真係長痛不如短痛<br />\n<br />\n我好鍾意你 但我諗我真係要放手啦<br />\n我會忍住唔搵你<br />\n祝你幸福"},{"pid":"a619791ae39f837065208f29f05a30b1352e4a9a","tid":2298260,"uid":132160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"一齊互勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bfab9886fb4376e7be4b49449205fffaf0da5e","tid":2298260,"uid":201604,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"勉你老母 咪能ff啦"},{"pid":"b517ed7253c7fd14084e3b1e07e32b34adbd438a","tid":2298260,"uid":132160,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"我真係試過不求回報咁去愛 但原來我變到愈黎愈貪心<br />\n開始想要承諾 開始想要永遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fada4b72f5b8ceef00903d31f18dc323cf5c29","tid":2298260,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b517ed7253c7fd14084e3b1e07e32b34adbd438a","tid":2298260,"uid":132160,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"我真係試過不求回報咁去愛 但原來我變到愈黎愈貪心<br />\n開始想要承諾 開始想要永遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係咩事？同對方冇辦法一齊？"},{"pid":"ef06cbcc2275877e0b35dd8cabe6a4370f27c7d4","tid":2298260,"uid":283310,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:0